ygData.messageBody:
Hi,
Yes, it has been quiet. I play Addie Healnbear a level 27 cleric (and a few
other baby characters) on Tunare. I'm currently in SK hunting outside of
Paw. I seem to be forever stuck on 27 right now. It is just a little bad
luck. I get ahead and a cyclops sneaks up, then too many gnolls for my group
to handle, etc. Then real life calls and I log behind in skill unstead of
ahead. I know she will get over the hump soon. I really want some of those
29 spells ). Also getting to the point where I can go and pay back those
Sand Gaints that would womp me in Oasis.

Jane
